snippet.title: Hero Emblems II  Boss Battle and Cutscene footage (In-Development)
snippet.description:
The video shows the latest development progress of HE2, which includes 2 parts:
The first part is the BOSS battle. 
The second part is the cutscene-then-battle. 

HE2 music is produced by Shi Kuang Lee.
